caveats:
2022-04-13: In the 6th round of data collection the Health and FSCL clusters partially anonymised some partner names, which are excluded from the count of partners and breakdown per type.

Prior to 2022-04-13: As Protection and Shelter Clusters don’t share their partners’ names operating at Non-government controlled areas, the table does not include information on Protection and Shelter Cluster partners operating in NGCA of Donetska and Luhanska oblasts.
methodology_other: Collected by OCHA from partners through Clusters/Sectors
name: ukraine-who-does-what-where-3w
notes: Consolidated 3W and 5W data (Who does What, Where) from OCHA Ukraine, collected from the clusters and organizations involved in the response.
